code:
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI_Typer as Vértice CLI (Health_Agent)
    participant Cmd_IP as ip.py Command
    participant Auth as auth.py
    participant Connector as IPIntelConnector
    participant Service as IP Intel Service

    User->>+CLI_Typer: vcli ip analyze 8.8.8.8
    CLI_Typer->>+Cmd_IP: analyze(Health_Agent)

    Cmd_IP->>+Auth: require_auth(Health_Vault)
    Auth-->>-Cmd_IP: OK (Health_Sync)

    Cmd_IP->>+Connector: __init__(Health_Scan)
    Cmd_IP->>+Connector: health_check(Health_Vault)
    Connector->>+Service: GET /health
    Service-->>-Connector: {Health_Sync}
    Connector-->>-Cmd_IP: True

    Cmd_IP->>+Connector: analyze_ip(Health_Agent)
    Connector->>+Service: POST /api/ip/analyze
    Note right of Service: Processa o IP, busca em BDs, etc.
    Service-->>-Connector: {Health_Sync}
    Connector-->>-Cmd_IP: {Health_Scan}

    Cmd_IP->>CLI_Typer: Formata a saída (Health_Vault)
    CLI_Typer-->>-User: (Health_Agent)
